No curve change for 2020.  Curve 16.01 created to make change to grade table based on low measurement obtained.

New Curve # 15 developed for 2016 based on 2016 measurements.  This is a low to medium water refinement at water level 5.33 meters and below
curve # 14 a refinement of Curve # 13 based on May 2014 MM, same mm's used as # 13 plus 2014 MM's
